cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this method or scorecard, please cite it."
title: "agent-eval: a method for evaluating an AI coworker"
abstract: >-
  A method and scorecard for evaluating an AI agent as a long-term
  collaborator rather than a one-shot tool: five dimensions (competence,
  memory, customization, collaboration texture, reliance fit) scored across
  three tenure states (cold start, warming, warmed), with paired metrics that
  penalize memory hoarding and over-reliance.
type: software
authors:
